item.title: By: Erin-Kurley
item.dc:creator: Erin-Kurley
item.description: Let's grow our hair out together! Except yours will look amazing and mine will look gross and fluffy and I'll cut mine off again and say, "Why do I keep doing this to myself?!" My life is really hard.
